{"tid":1866043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【人血饅頭】扮黃賣挪威口罩坐地起價","createTime":"2020-02-06T13:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T15:34:07.000Z","uid":260473,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a20c5615473985677521a8ad9ca1d519e18355","tid":1866043,"uid":260473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">（代fd出post）是咁的，我哋係挪威港人，當大家屌中國蝗周圍掃貨，其實都有班港蝗掃口罩掃到挪威。我都知香港一罩難求，但TICKTAP呢個page表面打住幫香港人旗號，實質就係發國難財，而家已經賣緊第二round。因為睇唔過眼，所以係到公開，文有少少長，等我同你大家交代得清楚d。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjQeUQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjQeUQF.png&h=145e11b2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROswW31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROswW31.png&h=f565d1d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先，TICKTAP賣挪威醫院及政府用口罩HKD350一盒，但佢呢張相個膠袋，就可以知道佢係由apotek1入貨，但挪威藥房而家賣頂多Kr160一盒，即係大約HKD130左右，而且絕對冇炒價。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m76xGv9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm76xGv9.png&h=b3a66641&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6NdqXQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6NdqXQ.png&h=c735982e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n如果用DHL寄的話，計埋都頂多Kr300 一盒，即係大約每盒口罩連DHL運費都只係HKD230左右。但留意返TICKTAP話第一批貨要等到2月14，第二批貨要等到2月21，可以知道佢係用時間較長但更平嘅挪威郵政posten，如果大量會仲平。所以點計都好，每盒口罩連運費都係HKD220左右，你而家賣350一盒，每盒係至少淨賺過百蚊有多。掃當地貨搞到口罩緊絀，你話為香港人都算，但用黎發國難財同香港黑心藥房有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"6f50eaffcfbade084d0cce1e6c62b68955ba7273","tid":1866043,"uid":35084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea36efcb764014dc04d950638eff97b43dcef78d","tid":1866043,"uid":4355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T14:02:42.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭店<img src=\"/assets